reviewText: Three great movies in one dvd its amazing!
Don't buy this if you want the "too big to fit in here" song/dance scene from the sweetest thing . It doesn't have it.
Came in time but the box came like it was used
3 awesome movies for the money. Shipped quickly and I'm very happy with this purchase.
well made and holds my dvds so that i can find them and they are easy to put back. I will be purchasing another one for the rest of my movies
